== 生平 ==
丹妮絲在1998年自家鄉[[捷克斯洛伐克|捷克斯洛伐克]]搬至[[多倫多|多倫多]]，開始在[[脫衣舞|脫衣舞]]俱樂部工作。她的第一次演出是在2000年《North Pole 13》中與[[狄倫·戴|狄倫·戴]]（Dillon Day）的合作。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://avn.com/index.cfm?objectid=D7147661-0FCD-5672-11963F71C2B51D3D |title=Czech Mate: Nikita Denise Returns |accessdate=2008-02-03 |author=Nelson X |date=2008-02-01 |publisher=[[成人影帶新聞|AVN]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209010604/http://www.avn.com/index.cfm?objectID=D7147661-0FCD-5672-11963F71C2B51D3D |archivedate=2008-02-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url= http://xfanz.com/news/87932|title= Nikita Denise Visits Playboy Radio|accessdate= 2008-02-03|author= Tod Hunter|date= 2007-12-18|publisher= xfanz.com|archive-date= 2013-07-16|archive-url= https://www.webcitation.org/6I9YuFuVP?url=http://www.xfanz.com/|dead-url= no}}</ref>

2006年，妮姬塔獻出導演的處女作《Nikita's Extreme Idols》。這部片也是她休息超過一年後的首度演出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ainews.com/story/10150/|title=Nikita Denise Directorial Debut: Nikita's Extreme Idols|accessdate=2006-06-13|archive-date=2006-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060614233945/http://ainews.com/story/10150/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

